OL,3,CWelsh Labour pledges same-day mental
OL,4,Chealth services and a #2 bus fare cap
OL,6,FWelsh Labour leader Eluned Morgan says
OL,7,Fthe party will introduce easy-to-
OL,8,Faccess, same-day mental health
OL,9,Fservices if elected in May.
OL,11,FWith just over two months until the
OL,12,Felection, Eluned Morgan set out her
OL,13,Fparty's priorities for the campaign
OL,14,Fand her vision for a 'fairer future
OL,15,FWales'.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
