PN,46902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772647564
OL,3,CWelsh Labour pledges same-day mental
OL,4,Chealth services and a #2 bus fare cap
OL,6,FSpeaking at the launch in Newport, she
OL,7,Fsaid: "Fairness today cannot mean
OL,8,Fpermanent patience. It cannot mean
OL,9,F'bear with us'. It cannot mean 'it's
OL,10,Fcomplicated.' It cannot mean 'come
OL,11,Fback in five years.'
OL,13,F"Fairness today must mean progress you
OL,14,Fcan see, progress you can measure,
OL,15,Fprogress you can feel.
OL,17,F"That is the promise I am making
OL,18,Ftoday. That is the promise of this new
OL,19,Fchapter for Wales."
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
