PN,46903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772647564
OL,3,CWelsh Labour pledges same-day mental
OL,4,Chealth services and a #2 bus fare cap
OL,6,F"We will focus on the things that make
OL,7,Fthe biggest difference to daily life,
OL,8,Fand we will deliver them with the
OL,9,Fseriousness that government demands.
OL,10,FThe Labour Party, like the Chartists
OL,11,Fbefore us, would be nothing if it did
OL,12,Fnot represent the true needs of the
OL,13,Fpeople. Because slogans are easy.
OL,14,FRunning Wales is harder."
OL,16,FAs part of the launch, the Welsh
OL,17,FLabour leader announced a pledge to
OL,18,Ftransform mental healthcare to provide
OL,19,Feasy-to-access, same-day services so
OL,20,Feveryone can get the support they
OL,21,Fneed, when they need it.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
