OL,3,CWelsh Labour pledges same-day mental
OL,4,Chealth services and a #2 bus fare cap
OL,6,FBuilding on the success of services
OL,7,Flike 111 press 2, this new 'open
OL,8,Faccess' model of care will be tested
OL,9,Fby all health boards in demonstrator
OL,10,Fsites, making Wales the first country
OL,11,Fin the world to have such a system.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV Wales, sent direct
OL,16,Fto your inbox every Saturday morning.
OL,18,FEluned Morgan's speech set out further
OL,19,Fpolicies, covering health, education
OL,20,Fand the cost of living, adding to
OL,21,Fthose already announced which include:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
