OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1772647564
OL,3,CWelsh Labour pledges same-day mental
OL,4,Chealth services and a #2 bus fare cap
OL,6,FDirectly addressing opposition
OL,7,Fparties, Eluned Morgan said: "You
OL,8,Fcannot fix waiting times with a
OL,9,Fhashtag. You cannot grow wages on
OL,10,FTikTok. You cannot build a hospital
OL,11,Fwith a committee. You need a plan. You
OL,12,Fneed priorities. You need delivery.
OL,13,FThat's what Welsh Labour is offering."
